WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.237
=Episode 1=

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.200
(Liquor store)
(My name is Ye Chen.)

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:55.439
(For over 20 years,)

00:00:55.880 --> 00:00:57.200
(I have been an orphan.)

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:00.399
(Cuixuan Pavilion)
(A worthless, despised nobody.)

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:02.630
(In order to treat Madam Li,)

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:05.079
(I work eight jobs every day)

00:01:06.039 --> 00:01:07.799
(tirelessly from dawn to dusk.)

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.270
(I endure all kinds of humiliation.)

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.920
(But no one knows my true identity.)

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:19.040
(Money.)

00:01:19.799 --> 00:01:20.719
(Beautiful women.)

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:22.840
(Power.)

00:01:23.719 --> 00:01:25.239
Mr. Ye, please let me off the hook.

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:26.000
(I am)

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.760
(the heir of the top financial empire,
the Ye family.)

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:31.840
(It all started)

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.200
( a year ago,)

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.959
(the moment I became the Lucky Star.)

00:01:41.175 --> 00:01:42.850
(Jinzhou)

00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:48.840
The show begins,
featuring our very own clown.

00:01:49.537 --> 00:01:51.640
(Ye Chen, soon-to-be Lucky Star)
(This is Ye Chen.)

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:53.040
(Though an orphan,)

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.500
(he carries the spirit of a dragon.)

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:56.000
(Despite the harshness,)

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:57.640
(he has never)

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:59.950
(been broken by suffering.)

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:02.040
(The Xiao family's fortune has run dry.)

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:05.519
(Old Mrs. Xiao, family head)
(But if he marries)

00:02:05.519 --> 00:02:07.400
(into the family by 7 p.m. today,)

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:08.599
(he shall bring you wealth,)

00:02:08.599 --> 00:02:09.359
(and glory)

00:02:09.719 --> 00:02:11.079
(shall be reborn.)

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:13.799
Don't be shy. Come here.

00:02:14.175 --> 00:02:14.934
Is it fun?

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.520
Answer me. Is it fun?

00:02:18.840 --> 00:02:19.479
What's going on?

00:02:21.250 --> 00:02:22.840
You want money, right?

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.000
Here.

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:25.240
Take it.

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:26.919
Enough?

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.120
Want more?

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.439
How shameless.

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:34.680
- Lucky Star!
- Lucky Star!

00:02:36.919 --> 00:02:37.599
Go.

00:02:41.199 --> 00:02:42.120
What lucky star?

00:02:42.479 --> 00:02:43.719
Is it some sort of a scam?

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:04.400
The Lucky Star shall return.

00:03:07.687 --> 00:03:09.247
Don't bother trying.

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:13.719
Today's the day. Whether you

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:15.319
like it or not,

00:03:15.387 --> 00:03:15.800
(Happy Wedding)

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.759
you have to get married.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.199
Ma'am,

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:20.439
money can't buy me.

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.680
I won't marry you.

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:22.680
Marry me? You wish.

00:03:34.759 --> 00:03:36.000
(My name is Xiao Churan.)

00:03:36.250 --> 00:03:38.000
(No one can force me into anything.)

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:38.812
(Xiao Churan, heir to Xiao Group)

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:40.120
(I only came to see)

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:42.240
(who this Lucky Star really is.)

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:50.737
Xiao Churan

00:03:50.919 --> 00:03:52.520
(Memories)
of Civil Engineering

00:03:52.719 --> 00:03:54.719
is our campus belle

00:03:54.719 --> 00:03:57.080
and the eldest heir
of a leading construction enterprise

00:03:57.080 --> 00:03:59.080
in Jinzhou.

00:04:00.039 --> 00:04:01.520
You have no chance.

00:04:01.919 --> 00:04:03.000
I agree.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:03.590
I'll marry her.

00:04:04.199 --> 00:04:05.439
I'll do it.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:11.319
(She's stunning.)

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:13.240
(He seems dense.)

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:22.580
Pervert.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.120
There's... a loose thread.

00:04:27.062 --> 00:04:27.863
Lame.

00:04:28.959 --> 00:04:30.079
(Still the same temper.)

00:04:30.380 --> 00:04:31.639
There really is a loose thread.

00:04:32.020 --> 00:04:33.100
(Happy Wedding)
Grandma,

00:04:33.210 --> 00:04:34.360
can that clown inside really

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.600
change our family's fortune?

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.439
The master said so himself.

00:04:37.639 --> 00:04:39.759
As long as he marries
into the family before 7 p.m.,

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.720
our family will be saved from disaster

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:44.800
and rise to glory once more.

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:47.800
(Marriage Agreement)
Sign this

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.000
before we get married.

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:52.160
Looks like you came prepared.

00:04:52.279 --> 00:04:53.079
I'll take a look.

00:04:53.962 --> 00:04:57.001
(Marriage Agreement)
Both parties will only be married in name.

00:04:57.079 --> 00:04:59.560
You will sleep in separate beds.

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:02.000
No marital relations shall occur.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.800
Term. One year.

00:05:04.079 --> 00:05:05.519
Can you make it longer?

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:07.959
I'll sign.

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.850
(Party A: Xiao Churan, Party B: Ye Chen)

00:05:12.762 --> 00:05:14.087
(Happy Wedding)

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:17.279
A Lucky Star has entered the household.

00:05:17.537 --> 00:05:21.437
We Xiao family
will prosper from here on out!

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:29.360
Ye Chen,

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.439
what kind of son-in-law are you?

00:05:31.439 --> 00:05:33.079
You're nothing but a failure!

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:37.425
(I thought)

00:05:37.425 --> 00:05:39.505
(that a wonderful life
was about to begin.)

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:40.879
(Unexpectedly,)

00:05:40.879 --> 00:05:42.720
(Xiao Group's stock price plummeted.)

00:05:42.959 --> 00:05:45.240
(The Xiao family became
the biggest joke in Jinzhou.)

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.079
(And I)

00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:48.475
(became part of that joke as well.)

00:05:50.687 --> 00:05:53.162
(Birthday)

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:57.959
Sorry,

00:05:57.959 --> 00:05:58.959
we're late.

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:00.775
My e-bike ran out of battery on the way.

00:06:02.519 --> 00:06:03.319
Ye Chen.

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:05.560
Today is Grandma's 70th birthday.

00:06:05.759 --> 00:06:07.950
Finally a chance for you to shine,

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.375
and you show up late.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:10.560
Churan.

00:06:10.879 --> 00:06:12.879
Couldn't you have
picked a fancier restaurant?

00:06:12.987 --> 00:06:14.199
There's barely any food here.

00:06:14.519 --> 00:06:15.560
So stingy.

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:18.000
Churan, have a seat.

00:06:18.279 --> 00:06:18.959
Here.

00:06:22.399 --> 00:06:23.519
I'll sit here.

00:06:24.087 --> 00:06:25.200
(Birthday)

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:25.720
Mom.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:26.740
The more, the merrier.

00:06:28.759 --> 00:06:29.319
Grandma,

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:30.759
I'd like to give you

00:06:30.759 --> 00:06:33.120
(Premium Pu'er Tea)
this century-old Pu'er tea brick.

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:34.680
It's worth half a million.

00:06:34.937 --> 00:06:36.362
(Xiao Hailong,
Xiao Churan's little brother)

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:37.439
Grandma,

00:06:37.439 --> 00:06:38.519
Yunfei and I

00:06:38.519 --> 00:06:39.959
have specially prepared for you

00:06:39.959 --> 00:06:41.319
a top-grade Hetian jade Buddha.

00:06:41.519 --> 00:06:42.420
(Xiao Weiwei, Churan's little sister
Wang Yunfei, Weiwei's boyfriend)

00:06:42.420 --> 00:06:43.220
Worth 700,000.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.920
Lucky Star, your gift

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.639
must be incredibly valuable, right?

00:06:49.639 --> 00:06:50.920
Absolutely!

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:54.500
A gift from the Lucky Star
is bound to be priceless.

00:06:54.750 --> 00:06:56.639
Grandma,
I'll perform a little talent for you.

00:06:56.680 --> 00:06:57.720
The Bottle Flip Blitz.

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:27.040
How's it?

00:07:27.279 --> 00:07:28.319
Mr. Zhang is here.

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:33.839
Mr. Zhang.

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.000
Wenhao.

00:07:35.212 --> 00:07:37.000
(Zhang Wenhao, the Zhang family heir)

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:40.512
(Xiao Changkun, Xiao Churan's father)
Isn't he the punk

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:41.650
who used to harass our daughter?

00:07:41.731 --> 00:07:42.937
(Ma Lan, Xiao Churan's mother)
That's called courting.

00:07:44.399 --> 00:07:46.600
Churan, you're as beautiful as ever.

00:07:49.050 --> 00:07:51.810
A top-grade jade Buddha pendant.

00:07:51.810 --> 00:07:53.120
Worth three million.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.319
I wish Grandma a long life.

00:07:55.439 --> 00:07:56.839
Three million?

00:07:56.839 --> 00:07:57.925
I've got some inside news.

00:07:58.025 --> 00:08:00.160
Jinzhou's top conglomerate, Dihao Group,

00:08:00.170 --> 00:08:01.279
is about to launch a resort project

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:04.150
worth two billion.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:05.720
- Two billion?
- Two billion?

00:08:05.959 --> 00:08:06.920
I can

00:08:07.199 --> 00:08:10.399
take Churan to meet
with their chairperson, Wang Dongxue,

00:08:10.587 --> 00:08:13.748
and have him assign
the project to your family.

00:08:13.925 --> 00:08:15.125
With that two billion,

00:08:15.125 --> 00:08:17.625
our family can
turn things around completely.

00:08:17.712 --> 00:08:19.951
Turn things around?
This would be a massive comeback.

00:08:20.187 --> 00:08:23.137
It'd put you right back

00:08:23.137 --> 00:08:25.199
at the top of Jinzhou society.

00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:27.037
Thank you so much, Mr. Zhang.

00:08:27.075 --> 00:08:28.515
Hold on. Don't thank me just yet.

00:08:28.575 --> 00:08:31.037
Of course, there's a condition.

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:32.160
Churan must

00:08:32.480 --> 00:08:35.279
divorce that loser immediately

00:08:35.399 --> 00:08:36.160
and

00:08:36.575 --> 00:08:37.527
marry me.

00:08:38.250 --> 00:08:39.437
I don't care whether you

00:08:39.437 --> 00:08:40.837
are some overseas returnee.

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:42.437
Churan already has a husband.

00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:43.039
I say yes.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.919
You'll divorce him now.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:45.960
Mom?

00:08:46.159 --> 00:08:46.759
Ye Chen.

00:08:49.039 --> 00:08:50.240
Sign the papers. Now.

00:08:50.300 --> 00:08:51.341
And get out of the family.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.159
I disagree.

00:08:53.587 --> 00:08:54.227
Grandma.

00:08:54.840 --> 00:08:56.087
Why do you always pin your hopes

00:08:56.087 --> 00:08:57.519
on other people?

00:08:57.840 --> 00:08:59.720
As long as we just
stick together as a family,

00:08:59.720 --> 00:09:02.400
I believe the Xiao Group
will make a comeback.

00:09:02.512 --> 00:09:04.120
This is two billion.

00:09:04.639 --> 00:09:05.675
You're being naive.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:07.840
I also disagree.

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.000
Ye Chen.

00:09:13.937 --> 00:09:15.869
Do you want to save Madam Li or not?

00:09:17.580 --> 00:09:18.825
How do you know about Madam Li?

00:09:19.579 --> 00:09:21.800
I not only know that you, an orphan,

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:23.280
were raised by her,

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:26.212
but I also know
she has severe kidney disease.

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:29.000
All these years,
you've worked yourself to the bone,

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:30.799
doing menial, degrading jobs,

00:09:31.080 --> 00:09:32.399
all to pay for her treatment.

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:32.879
Right?

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.475
But do you know

00:09:34.475 --> 00:09:36.799
why you could never find a kidney donor

00:09:36.799 --> 00:09:38.450
and she could never have the surgery?

00:09:39.962 --> 00:09:41.937
It's because I won't allow it.

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:45.440
You a-hole!

00:09:48.799 --> 00:09:50.337
Listen to me and leave Churan.

00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:52.440
I can save Madam Li

00:09:52.687 --> 00:09:54.865
and give you one million.

00:09:55.725 --> 00:09:57.683
I'll find my own way to save her.

00:09:57.987 --> 00:10:00.012
I will never divorce Churan.

00:10:00.725 --> 00:10:02.237
You ungrateful piece of trash.

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:04.399
Throw him out!

00:10:04.679 --> 00:10:05.200
Grandma!

00:10:16.012 --> 00:10:16.990
Ye Chen!

00:10:17.100 --> 00:10:18.630
Churan, stay here.

00:10:18.879 --> 00:10:19.600
Stay here.

00:10:22.759 --> 00:10:25.120
You asked for it.

00:10:26.762 --> 00:10:30.525
(I won't allow
a live-in son-in-law to ruin my plan.)

00:10:35.112 --> 00:10:36.071
(Ye Chen,)

00:10:36.487 --> 00:10:37.846
(what kind of son-in-law are you?)

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:39.775
(You're nothing but a failure!)

00:10:42.039 --> 00:10:42.960
(You're a loser!)

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:43.759
(Get out.)

00:10:43.975 --> 00:10:45.494
(Get out of the family.)

00:10:49.039 --> 00:10:49.960
But do you know

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:52.639
why you could never find a kidney donor

00:10:52.639 --> 00:10:54.120
and she could never have the surgery?

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:56.080
It's because I won't allow it.

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:00.600
(I don't want to divorce Churan.)

00:11:02.799 --> 00:11:05.300
(Am I really just a failure?)

00:11:23.039 --> 00:11:23.820
- Mr. Ye.
- Mr. Ye.

00:11:39.662 --> 00:11:41.902
I read the script exactly
as you wrote it.

00:11:41.987 --> 00:11:43.426
Not a single mistake.

00:11:45.012 --> 00:11:46.800
I lied again.

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:49.900
Punish me.

00:11:50.050 --> 00:11:53.987
♪Yet no one
sees the grace within my tears♪

00:12:08.812 --> 00:12:11.300
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:12:11.387 --> 00:12:15.140
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:20.537
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:12:20.700 --> 00:12:22.987
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:23.300 --> 00:12:25.980
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:27.050 --> 00:12:29.675
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:29.975 --> 00:12:32.987
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:33.187 --> 00:12:36.237
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:36.350 --> 00:12:39.312
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:12:39.580 --> 00:12:42.737
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:12:42.962 --> 00:12:46.712
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:12:46.712 --> 00:12:49.575
♪I belong to no one♪

00:12:49.637 --> 00:12:53.087
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:12:53.087 --> 00:12:55.762
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:12:55.762 --> 00:13:02.100
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪